text: Sanusi Tjokroadiredjo (born 26 May 1925) is an Indonesian former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Indonesian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Indonesia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Magelang Category:Sportspeople from Central Java
